'''耶涯大坝'''（{{lang-my|ရဲရွာ တာတမံ}}）是[[缅甸|缅甸]]目前已经竣工的最大的水电站项目，属于缅甸的国家重点工程，号称“缅甸的三峡工程”。坐落在距[[曼德勒|曼德勒]]直线距离52公里的[[皎克西鎮|皎克西鎮]]耶瓦村附近[[米界河|米界河]]，总装机容量790兆瓦（79万千瓦，4台发电机组），由[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]帮助建成，2011年11月全部建成并网发电并全部由[[中国水电|中国水电]]移交缅甸。为碾压混凝土重力坝（RCC），坝顶高程197米，最大坝高137米，顶宽12米，溢流堰顶高程185米。<ref name="speed">{{cite web |url=http://www.waterpowermagazine.com/story.asp?storyCode=2049274 |title=Feature - The need for speed |work=Water Power Magazine |publisher=Burma Rivers Network |accessdate=10 February 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110614043444/http://www.waterpowermagazine.com/story.asp?storyCode=2049274 |archivedate=2011年6月14日 }}</ref> <ref name="BL">{{cite book  |author=U. Win Kyaw, U. Myint Zaw, Alan Dredge, Paul Fischer, K. Steiger  |title=Yeywa Hydropower Project, an Overview  |editor=Department of Hydropower, Ministry of Electric Power, Myanmar & Colenco Power Engineering Ltd, CH  |publisher=Burma Library  |url=http://www.burmalibrary.org/docs4/Yeywa%20profile.pdf  |access-date=2014-07-14  |archive-date=2010-12-13  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101213065623/http://burmalibrary.org/docs4/Yeywa%20profile.pdf  |dead-url=no  }}</ref><ref name="YHP">{{cite web |url=http://www.burmariversnetwork.org/burmese/images/stories/documents/yeywaoverview.pdf |title=Yeywa Hydropower Project,  an Overview |author=Win Kyaw, Myint Zaw, Alan Dredge, Paul Fischer, K. Steiger |publisher=Vietnam National Commission On Large Dams |accessdate=9 February 2010 |archive-date=2011-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110428034811/http://www.burmariversnetwork.org/burmese/images/stories/documents/yeywaoverview.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

